description.value: get the phone id from sec address
get sec account ID by external ID (c4c AccountID)
the customer does not exist on cec so create it
Receives the notification from c4c on create/update of individual customer
gets the authentication token from token generator
get the BP id from SEC by external id
Delete email as email is deleted from c4c
